Subset of the output differentiated by diaganosis
```{r}
MEL<-subset(output,Label == "MEL")
NEV<-subset(output, Label == "NEV")
SEK<-subset(output, Label == "SEK")
```




Symmetry:
```{r}
Sym_MLE<-(MEL$Symmetry)
NEV_mean_sym<-mean(MEL$Symmetry)
NEV_sd_sym<-sd(MEL$Symmetry)
```

```{r}
Sym_nev<-(NEV$Symmetry)
NEV_mean_sym<-mean(NEV$Symmetry)
NEV_sd_sym<-sd(NEV$Symmetry)

```


```{r}
Sym_sek<-(SEK$Symmetry)
SEK_mean_sym<-mean(SEK$Symmetry)
SEK_sd_sym<-sd(SEK$Symmetry)


```


```{r}
t.test(Sym_MLE,Sym_nev)
t.test(Sym_sek,Sym_nev)
t.test(Sym_sek,Sym_MLE)
```
